{"id":232555409,"title":"希望我們的將來都能保持善良","content":"我們都知道在這個領域裡面總是會發生一堆認真以外的鳥事，舉凡實習遇到老師不合理針對、職場遇到同事欺壓、頂頭上司換位置換腦袋and so on\n\n\n但能做什麼...離開嗎？\n\n也許離開會很舒服啦 但那些惡瘤依然會存在\n\n我在高護實習的某梯有位老師對我說過：\n\n我知道你們覺得實習壓力很大，我們也是那樣過\n來的，而且我們那個年代遭遇更多不合理的事情，但我不希望你們在還是幼苗的階段就被扼殺，所以不管你們以後會不會進入這個行業，要保持你的善良。\n\n最近實習遇到了很多事情心情很低落\n\n但我相信護理的價值不在於被欺壓！\n\n大家會更好的！\nhttps://i.imgur.com/xCmu13C.jpg","excerpt":"我們都知道在這個領域裡面總是會發生一堆認真以外的鳥事，舉凡實習遇到老師不合理針對、職場遇到同事欺壓、頂頭上司換位置換腦袋and so on，但能做什麼...離開嗎？也許離開會很舒服啦 但那些惡瘤依然會","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"b22d2f5d-3c06-4d08-96b8-770eb38e8f96","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-11-23T05:53:32.451Z","updatedAt":"2019-11-23T05:53:32.451Z","commentCount":7,"likeCount":101,"tags":[],"topics":["護理","希望"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"護理","forumAlias":"nursing","school":"慈濟科技大學","department":"護理系","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":101}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/xCmu13C.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"d1eeadf5-6ce4-4736-be2f-4bea2ce1249b","url":"https://i.imgur.com/xCmu13Cl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/xCmu13Cl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/xCmu13Cl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-11-23T05:53:32.451Z","updatedAt":"2019-11-23T05:53:32.451Z"},{"id":"d1eeadf5-6ce4-4736-be2f-4bea2ce1249b","url":"https://i.imgur.com/xCmu13C.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/xCmu13C","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/xCmu13Cl.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-11-23T05:53:32.451Z","updatedAt":"2019-11-23T05:53:32.451Z"}],"postAvatar":""}